About this item

  • Smart remote control mode: The remote control adopts 2.4ghz transmission technology, which is sensitive to control and ultra-long distance control. And yet another amazing remote control watch. Wear the watch on your hand, change your posture, and the deformable car can sense your posture changes, drive and change at will.
  • Off-Road Multi-Roller Tires: This 4WD RC monster truck is equipped with unique roller traction tires. Off-road mode tackles any terrain - sand, grass, dirt, rocks and more.
  • Crazy stunts and cool features: 1:12 scale remote car can move in all directions, can do 360 rotation and double-sided driving, and the four-wheel-drive climbing stunt car has light and music effects and can travel on both sides. Cool functions and unlimited fun give children wonderful operation experience and visual effects.
  • Included Safe Rechargeable Battery: The car is equipped with a rechargeable upgraded 3.7V (1300mAh) battery - a high-capacity high-speed power battery for long-lasting durability. 50-60 minutes of use on a two-hour charge. The remote uses two "1.5V" AA batteries (not included).
  • Best Gift Ideas: 2.4G Stunt Gesture Sensing Twist Buggy with Lights, Music, Drift Traversing, Remote Control, Dancing and more, Creative Birthday Party Gifts for Boys and Girls, Perfect Back to School Gift for Kids, Halloween/Christmas/Giving Your children's day gift or stress relief toy..
